title: The numbers behind “natural” birth control
description: Videos on TikTok have been claiming that so-called “natural” birth control methods can be 99% effective. We examine what we really know, and how we know it.
itunes:subtitle: We examine online claims about the effectiveness of “natural” birth control methods
